      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more descriptive about the actual people he's seeing and how they appear to him? like, how he compares their appearance or their lack of technology to the \"advancement\" of Europe. make it feel like he's looking down on them as being almost animalistic or just totally lost without guidance.",
